  <brief_title>Aggressive Versus Moderate Glycemic Control in Diabetic Coronary Bypass Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact of Aggressive Versus Moderate Glycemic Control on Clinical Outcomes Following Coronary Artery Bypass Graft Surgery in Diabetic Patients</official_title>
